A containerized Flask REST API for ad campaign analytics, utilizing Redis for query caching.

API Endpoints
Results are cached in Redis for 30-300 seconds.

GET /campaign/<id>/performance - Returns CTR, impressions, clicks, and total ad cost.

GET /advertiser/<id>/spending - Returns total spending for a specific advertiser.

GET /user/<id>/engagements - Returns the click history for a specific user.

The API will be available at: http://localhost:5000
